oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Ray Whitley Program - 1969-08-01 Programs: IX-XIV
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The recording is of Ray Whitley (musician/entertainer) and his Six-Bar Cowboys (musical group) performances for multiple entertainment pieces. The recordings feature a number of unidentified pieces. The tape was gathered on August 01, 1969. Tape is labeled as reel two, programs IX-XIV.
